    "In CV-free enhanced sampling techniques predefined CVs are not required as well as prior knowledge about the studied process (Liao 2020).",
    "For example, in popular REMD, multiple simulations run simultaneously at different temperatures or potential energy functions, with correlation reduced by exchanging conformations/temperatures between replicates at regular time intervals to avoid trapping the simulation in a stable conformation (Fig. 3) (Chen 2021; Liao 2020).",
